actions.message:
```
!fHelp                      Lists available commands
!fKick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
!fBan [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
!fMute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user
!fUnmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
!fDeleteChannel [#channel]  Deletes the mentioned channel
!fDeleteRole [#channel]     Deletes the mentioned role
```
